e\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"the true heart\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"the bends\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4156}, {\"ngram\": \"straits\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4168}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic officials\", \"from\": 4175, \"to\": 4192}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"the scores\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4241}, {\"ngram\": \"police officers\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4260}, {\"ngram\": \"security guards\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4277}, {\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 4282, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"its banks\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One man, in one boat, told me: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis river,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d the man said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthis is my life!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He stopped there, then added, with a dismissing wave, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou go now.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d As with the clean-up of the Thames before the London 2012 Games, the argument for sanitizing the Seine was not to clean up the river for the Olympics but for life afterward.\", \"from\": 4316, \"to\": 4650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4574, \"end\": 4579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.568394541193505e-38, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One man\", \"from\": 4316, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"one boat\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis river\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4360}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthis\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"my life!\